Naming Convention
Salesforce API Naming Convention
Recommended naming convention is to use the customer name in the prefix (WERFEN – WE) and include the project stream:

Sales – SAL: WESAL_
Service – SER: WESER_
Field Service – FSE: WEFSE_
Marketing Cloud – MKT: WEMKT_
Revenue Cloud – REV: WEREV_
If the functionality is cross‑module, the prefix must use the common value WERFEN_.

Following the prefix, a distinction will be made based on the component type.

